<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>عَنْهُمْ عن الكفار.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>[سورة الصافات <span class="c2">(٣٧)</span> : الآيات ١٧٩ الى ١٨٢]<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَأَبْصِرْ فَسَوْفَ يُبْصِرُونَ <span class="c2">(١٧٩)</span> سُبْحانَ رَبِّكَ رَبِّ الْعِزَّةِ عَمَّا يَصِفُونَ <span class="c2">(١٨٠)</span> وَسَلامٌ عَلَى الْمُرْسَلِينَ <span class="c2">(١٨١)</span> وَالْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ رَبِّ الْعالَمِينَ <span class="c2">(١٨٢)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>١٧٩-<span class="c5"> وَأَبْصِرْ فَسَوْفَ يُبْصِرُونَ:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَأَبْصِرْ وترقب.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>يُبْصِرُونَ العذاب.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>١٨٠-<span class="c5"> سُبْحانَ رَبِّكَ رَبِّ الْعِزَّةِ عَمَّا يَصِفُونَ:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>سُبْحانَ رَبِّكَ تنزيه لله تعالى.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>رَبِّ الْعِزَّةِ الذي بيده العزة والغلبة.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>عَمَّا يَصِفُونَ عما ينعتونه به من المفتريات.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>١٨١-<span class="c5"> وَسَلامٌ عَلَى الْمُرْسَلِينَ:</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>وَسَلامٌ وأمن وتحية.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>عَلَى الْمُرْسَلِينَ من اخترناهم رسلا.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>١٨٢-<span class="c5"> وَالْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ رَبِّ الْعالَمِينَ:</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>وَالْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ والثناء لله.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>رَبِّ الْعالَمِينَ خالق الوجود كله.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>